# {repo_name}

本仓库使用面向 Codex 的 repo-local workflow，durable state 位于 [`{sdd_dir}/`](./{sdd_dir}/)。

## 从这里开始

- agent 规则入口：[`AGENTS.md`](./AGENTS.md)
- workflow 说明：[`{sdd_dir}/workflow.md`](./{sdd_dir}/workflow.md)
- Process Summary：[`{sdd_dir}/docs/process.md`](./{sdd_dir}/docs/process.md)
- 项目进度：[`{sdd_dir}/docs/progress.md`](./{sdd_dir}/docs/progress.md)

## 日常命令

```sh
./{sdd_dir}/scripts/session-brief.sh
./{sdd_dir}/scripts/validate-sdd.sh --strict
./{sdd_dir}/scripts/new-task.sh "描述下一项变更"
```

```powershell
./{sdd_dir}/scripts/session-brief.ps1
./{sdd_dir}/scripts/validate-sdd.ps1 -Strict
./{sdd_dir}/scripts/new-task.ps1 "描述下一项变更"
```
